{"tid":609170,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（肥都有罪）南韓青年為逃兵役　半年增肥逾60磅，判處入獄5年","createTime":"2018-03-28T22:08:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-09T06:40:51.000Z","uid":22675,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"70a84df197f18df2d348990e4e7f6bc3f0bd7798","tid":609170,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T22:08:58.000Z","msg":"南韓一名青年前年被軍方揭發企圖增肥逾60磅，使自己的身體狀況不符軍方標準，以便避過服兵役。他在周日（25日）被判罪成，判處入獄5年，緩刑執行。<br />\n<br />\n據南韓傳媒報道，該名21歲青年於2016年2月時的身高為5呎9吋，體重為187磅。軍方於7月時為他進行第2次身體檢查，發覺他的體重暴增至250磅，體重指標（BMI）達到36.1，他其後獲改派公共服務部門任職。<br />\n<br />\n軍方其後查出該名青年故意增肥逃避兵役，遂落案起訴。法院在判詞中表示，該名青年故意增肥，以便讓自己逃過兵役的責任，遂判他罪成。該名青年隨後再次接受身體檢查，並表明願意加入軍隊。"},{"pid":"70b1df8b4c173d40aabeb0b3b15f83c0a8727d5f","tid":609170,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T22:11:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2GCoXPk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2GCoXPk&d=GRi6ROCj8D%2BfclimXTcDigCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=765146cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2GCoXPk</a>"},{"pid":"297e27de1731e2105ecfddb242e4f34ca3055e76","tid":609170,"uid":42407,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T22:17:22.000Z","msg":"😅"},{"pid":"840b427c645b0e3791fe745c9f2dd3422be2ece3","tid":609170,"uid":10890,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T22:37:46.000Z","msg":"呢啲擺撚明係衰懶醒周圍揚啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n慌唔係用圍同人講自己點避開啲辛苦野咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"971302ffd8a98b0c8756642185f9e3c84f62352d","tid":609170,"uid":40804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T22:42:23.000Z","msg":"拎條命嚟較飛都罰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n半年增咁多 勁撚過拍戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37572abc569c6d4abac8dcf78d7f7861fff674f5","tid":609170,"uid":42283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"